Reverting edit — This intro is faithful to the definition that the club uses to define itself (ARTICLE 1 - FC Barcelona's official statutes). If you do not agree with this definition, you should comment on the Talk page, since you are reverting a reliable sourced edit — See FC Barcelona official statutes.
